{"tid":2155923,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"認向梁晃維吐口水、拳打港大學生　中年漢判 120 小時社服令","createTime":"2020-08-14T06:01:34.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-14T06:05:53.000Z","uid":339805,"like":2,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"bb77349223dba600c85e628f3f7d744feb386d04","tid":2155923,"uid":339805,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-14T06:01:34.000Z","msg":"現任中西區區議員梁晃維去年與一班學生在港鐵葵芳站外派發「三罷」宣傳單張期間，遭一名中年漢三度吐口水襲擊，其中一名男學生更被拳打胸口。涉事的中年漢早前承認兩項普通襲擊罪，西九龍裁判法院主任裁判官羅德泉今日（14日）判處被告 120 小時社會服務令。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/politics/認向梁晃維吐口水-拳打港大學生-中年漢判-120-小時社服令/?fbclid=IwAR2uaCLEerni9Jo5-UrhEjsTYKorHWejpBKZapz2Yj2oNfYMIxd7TTV63Po\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%E8%AA%8D%E5%90%91%E6%A2%81%E6%99%83%E7%B6%AD%E5%90%90%E5%8F%A3%E6%B0%B4-%E6%8B%B3%E6%89%93%E6%B8%AF%E5%A4%A7%E5%AD%B8%E7%94%9F-%E4%B8%AD%E5%B9%B4%E6%BC%A2%E5%88%A4-120-%E5%B0%8F%E6%99%82%E7%A4%BE%E6%9C%8D%E4%BB%A4%2F%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR2uaCLEerni9Jo5-UrhEjsTYKorHWejpBKZapz2Yj2oNfYMIxd7TTV63Po&d=Bi55TGPCxKeiDoZ%2FBZgBR0B1UtkZy1G9%2FYekDAkGV2Y%3D&h=bb66bacc\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%E8%AA%8D%E5%90%91%E6%A2%81%E6%99%83%E7%B6%AD%E5%90%90%E5%8F%A3%E6%B0%B4-%E6%8B%B3%E6%89%93%E6%B8%AF%E5%A4%A7%E5%AD%B8%E7%94%9F-%E4%B8%AD%E5%B9%B4%E6%BC%A2%E5%88%A4-120-%E5%B0%8F%E6%99%82%E7%A4%BE%E6%9C%8D%E4%BB%A4%2F%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR2uaCLEerni9Jo5-UrhEjsTYKorHWejpBKZapz2Yj2oNfYMIxd7TTV63Po&h=adf4a475\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.thestandnews.com/politics/認向梁晃維吐口水-拳打港大學生-中年漢判-120-小時社服令/?fbclid=IwAR2uaCLEerni9Jo5-UrhEjsTYKorHWejpBKZapz2Yj2oNfYMIxd7TTV63Po</a>"},{"pid":"1d463f184e14e8512732b6f3474ea1a580e72203","tid":2155923,"uid":41116,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-14T06:02:27.000Z","msg":"又係d支那樣"},{"pid":"f247f6d0f95d10a4469ae1055e8d3e7bfcbfc6e8","tid":2155923,"uid":4493,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-14T06:03: